								</svg>
							</div>
							<div class="contact-details">
								<h3>Location</h3>
								<span class="contact-text">Palo Alto, CA</span>
								<p>Available for local meetups and Bay Area opportunities</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="availability">
						<h3>Current Status</h3>
						<div class="status-card">
							<div class="status-indicator active"></div>
							<div class="status-info">
								<h4>Open to Opportunities</h4>
								<p>Actively seeking <strong>summer 2025 internships</strong> in software engineering, AI/ML, or research positions. Also available for collaborative projects and freelance work.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.contact-hero {
		padding: 3rem 0 4rem;
		background: #fafaf8;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	.page-title {
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #2a2a2a;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.page-subtitle {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		color: #6a6a6a;
		max-width: 700px;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.contact-content {
		padding: 3rem 0 4rem;
		background: #fafaf8;
	}

	.contact-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
		align-items: start;
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.contact-info h2 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: #2a2a2a;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.contact-description {
		color: #6a6a6a;
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.contact-methods {
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.contact-method {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		padding: 0;
		background: transparent;
		transition: none;
	}

	.contact-icon {
		flex-shrink: 0;
		width: 40px;
		height: 40px;
		background: transparent;
		border: 1px solid #d4d4d4;
		border-radius: 4px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		color: #2a2a2a;
	}

	.contact-details h3 {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		color: #2a2a2a;
		margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	.contact-link {
		color: #2a2a2a;
		text-decoration: underline;
		font-weight: 400;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.contact-link:hover {
		color: #6a6a6a;
	}

	.contact-text {
		color: #2a2a2a;
		font-weight: 400;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.contact-details p {
		color: #8a8a8a;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.availability {
		background: transparent;
		border: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: 1.5rem;
	}

	.availability h3 {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: #2a2a2a;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	.status-card {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		align-items: flex-start;
	}

	.status-indicator {
		width: 8px;
		height: 8px;
		margin-top: 0.4rem;
		flex-shrink: 0;
		background: #2a2a2a;
	}

	.status-indicator.active {
		background: #2a2a2a;
		box-shadow: none;
	}

	.status-info h4 {
		color: #2a2a2a;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	.status-info p {
		color: #6a6a6a;
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.interests-connect {
		padding: 3rem 0 4rem;
		background: #fafaf8;
		border-top: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
	}

	.section-title {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		color: #2a2a2a;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.interests-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.interest-item {
		background: transparent;
		border: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
	}

	.interest-item:hover {
		border-color: #2a2a2a;
	}

	.interest-item h3 {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: #2a2a2a;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	.interest-item p {
		color: #6a6a6a;
		line-height: 1.7;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.page-title {
			font-size: 1.75rem;
		}

		.contact-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2.5rem;
		}

		.contact-method {
			gap: 0.75rem;
		}

		.status-card {
			gap: 0.75rem;
		}

		.interests-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.container {
			padding: 0 1rem;
		}
	}
</style>